{"type": "article", "id": 26157, "title": "H&M 开第 4000 家店，以及，Madewell 夏季穿搭手册不错｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。\r\n", "date": "2016-04-28T10:52:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1097, "name": "百货"}, {"id": 10407, "name": "限量"}, {"id": 6579, "name": "春夏系列"}, {"id": 1241, "name": "男装"}, {"id": 10104, "name": "开店"}, {"id": 12311, "name": "水桶包"}, {"id": 4489, "name": "代言"}, {"id": 17963, "name": "Madewell"}, {"id": 1066, "name": "Calvin Klein"}, {"id": 3350, "name": "Louis Vuitton"}, {"id": 1980, "name": "Topshop"}, {"id": 329, "name": "宝洁"}, {"id": 26901, "name": "JC Penney"}, {"id": 1060, "name": "H&M"}, {"id": 1081, "name": "丝芙兰"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 74, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702133737LmG8ST0XvHozk1aJ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://sg.fashionmag.com/news/H-M-opens-4-000th-store-in-India,687167.html#rc\"><b>H&amp;M 开第 4000 家店</b></a>｜瑞典快时尚巨头 H&amp;M 近日开了全球第 4000 家店，位于印度的 Noida 地区，四层楼的店铺占据 37000 平方英尺，开业当天有超过 500 位顾客排队。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://sg.fashionmag.com/news/JC-Penney-to-open-60-new-Sephora-locations,686977.html#rc\"><b>JC Penney  百货将新开 60 家丝芙兰</b></a>｜彭尼百货（JC Penney ）和美妆连锁店丝芙兰（Sephora）庆祝合作 10 周年，丝芙兰将在 JC Penney 新开 60 家新门店，而其中约一半以上的店铺将在 4 月 29 日开幕，其余的在 6 月 17 日，希望在关键的开学和度假时期之前获得足够的市场占有率。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/beauty-industry-news/financial/pg-beauty-sales-decline-5-in-quarter-10418389/\"><b>宝洁美容产品销售额下跌 5%</b></a>｜即使提价了 2%，宝洁（Procter &amp; Gamble）公司的美容产品净销售额还是在三季度有 5% 的下跌。Olay 抵消了 SK-II 的强劲表现。集团季度净收益与去年同期相比增加了 27%  至 27.8 亿美元，季度收入达到 33.1 亿美元，上涨了 10%。而整体的净销售额下跌了 7% 至 157.6 亿美元。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://fashionista.com/2016/04/topshop-wearable-tech\"><b>Topshop 也将开发可穿戴设备</b></a>｜英国零售商 Topshop 近日宣布将与投资伙伴 L Marks 共同开始 “Top Pitch” 计划，四周的时间将邀请全球的科技企业家和初创企业，申请名为“boot camp” 的活动，其中提供导师、工作坊、专家和 Topshop 高管的演示。最终被选中的队伍将获得在 Topshop 售卖产品的机会，以及老板 Philip Green 的投资。据悉，参与竞争的产品需是时髦且具有功能性的可穿戴设备，同时价格合理。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://sg.fashionmag.com/news/Lady-Gaga-and-Sir-Elton-John-Join-Macy-s-Celebrity-Lineup,687022.html#rc\"><b>Lady Gaga 和 Elton John 将与梅西百货合作</b></a>｜梅西百货 （Macy）周三宣布将和格莱美偶像歌手 Lady Gaga 及 Elton John 合作，推出 Love Bravery 限量服装线，这是梅西百货美国偶像（American Icons ）活动的一部分，包括衬衫、外套、手包、背包、围巾、帽子、钥匙扣、滑板、水杯等等。其中 25% 的收入将资助 Lady Gaga 的 Born This Way 基金会和 Elton John 的艾滋基金会。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133723Ay08FUqjTSmMJ74V.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.20980392\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133723eCi8glP3W2naXsLM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/madewell-summer-accessories-shoes/\">Madewell 最新的夏季潮流手册以 “Accessories First”（配饰当先）为主题</a>，看起来很悠闲：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133724tov1afnd487JWT65.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67011278\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133724Z5rb7JwQXD93insF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67011278\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133725eKkHL1ICxM07zl3X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133725akx41ihRVYBuCK5Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133726F0JkbRcZy3MY5Cn1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/4/kith-spring-2-2016-lookbook\">KITH 发布第二个春季男装系列</a>：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133726AoKpZV1UgbHyzlSW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133727s4tdoHRzNCe6U9gp.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021337270PCRm43t129alvcL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133728JwveXFfqD0H6bp1G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133728mPtjKvL9cSC4FO6M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">Louis Vuitton 发布最新旅行主题的广告，法国女演员 Léa Seydoux（主演《阿黛尔的生活》）出镜，她在 1 月宣布成为 LV 新大使，广告将出现在全球杂志的六月、七月刊上。此前她一直为 Miu Miu、Prada 拍摄。</p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133729pywWGl3BsH296uzb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133729mfkZbWMzQ8RH3BLl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66774194\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021337303KLOUvsCaPmxcJBX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133730aoDnf8ybUiOmsQMj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/calvin-klein-jeans-limited-edition-2016-campaign/\">Calvin Klein Jeans 在沙滩拍摄了最新系列大片</a>：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133731aSx7qz1bmRpyjGJF.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133732FU94pjMmreOC7coA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133732bE0Cf91gT2tZJuBw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">Bottega Veneta 推出最新水桶包：<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133733VidLZu2gWbf08jl1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64722222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133734i49qHAlGXBVr6QF0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.58148148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"> <a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/polo-ralph-lauren-spring-2016-clothes-shop/\">POLO Ralph Lauren 夏日特辑</a>：<br></p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021337345Akl2mOGDXxn1ELy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021337353gBbMCXkl9NZr81m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021337356Hgq4vKoDSpCWjn1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133736xILBk1PsVwDh6mco.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133736UxHJVeGgzPkiQ4Y5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133737zs5CyiDSUeHpxKf2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6425\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n\n"}